		You may want to get a list of English-speaking foreign doctors from the
		</p>
		<ul style="list-style-type:none;">
			<li>International Association for Medical Assistance to Travelers (IAMAT)</li>
			<li>1623 Military Road, #279</li>
			<li>Niagara Falls, NY 14304 (<a href="#" onclick="window.open('http://www.iamat.org', '_blank', 'toolbar=yes,location=yes,directories=yes,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes')">www.iamat.org</a>).</li>
