		<p>
		IAMAT can be reached at 716-754-4883. If an emergency occurs while you are traveling and you do not have such a list, contact the American Consulate, American Express, or local medical schools for a list of doctors.
		</p>
		<p>
		No matter where you go, wear a medical ID bracelet or necklace that shows you have diabetes. If you are leaving the country, also learn how to say &amp;quot;I have diabetes&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;sugar or orange juice, please&amp;quot; in the language or languages of the countries you will visit.
